* sudo add-apt-repository ppa:lightdm-team/crowd-greeter<br>
* sudo apt-get update &amp;&amp; sudo apt-get install crowd-greeter<br>
* sudo edit /etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf<br>
* Set ‘greeter-session=crowd-greeter’ in [SeatDefaults] section.<br>
